==English==
===Verb===
To kidnap [[Pacific Island]]ers or [[Kanaka]]s for work on, or sale to, [[plantation]]s - usually [[sugar]] plantations in [[Queensland]], [[Australia]]. From [[blackbird]] - ref. to the colour of the people. 

Variant - (to) '''blackbird'''

===Derived terms===

===Noun===
